Place your wallpaper images in this directory.

The default wallpaper path is referenced in labwc/autostart.
To use a custom wallpaper:

  1. Copy your image to this directory (or anywhere else)
  2. Or set via: echo "/path/to/wallpaper" > ~/.config/labwc/wallpaper
  3. Or use the wallpaper GUI: ./run_wallpaper_gui.sh

Recommended formats: PNG, JPG, WebP
Recommended resolution: at least 1920x1080
